      "created_at": "2021-06-02T21:11:04.533Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Honestly, I am not going for the Ragbrai this year. Its July last week. I am hoping to be fit enough next year to be able to participate in the next year\u2019s Ragbrai.</p>\n<p>I will check out Chris\u2019 book. I did come across him but in a negative way. The reason being not regarding the training approach per se, but regarding his bashing of the ketogenic diet/fat adapted diet.</p>\n<p>Thanks for pointing out another book in my way.</p>",
