      "created_at": "2021-06-03T07:36:33.830Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I was a very strong believer in the keto approach and even though the science seems solid I am questioning it as I feel it\u2019s easy to drive a poor way of eating (at least for me). I still strongly believe fat adapted can be beneficial and carb intolerance is a problem for most or all overweight people. All I really know is this stuff is seriously complex and the answer is usually \u201cit depends.\u201d  I think training is much simpler than diet <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>",
